<s> The IETF did not turn out to be the right place to do this work.  </s>
<s> The work on an XML format for encoding process information has been carried on by the WfMC in a new spec called Wf-XML.  </s>
<s> This is a subset of the original SWAP proposal, but the working group is pledged to proceed to fill in the rest of the functionality.  </s>
<s> SWAP then becomes simply the sending of this format over HTTP, which is an example transport protocol mentioned in the spec.  </s>
<s> check http://www.wfmc.org/ for details and to get a copy of the spec.  </s>
